<h3>Information</h3>
<div class="paddedcontent">This package recognises three types of operating system, the type of software that visitors are using on their computers to run all their applications.  The combination of this operating system with the software designed to run on it is known as a platform, an important concept when creating websites and web applications, because it is important to ensure that the website or application will work and display correctly on the platform favoured by your users.</div>
<div class="paddedcontent">Almost all websites to a greater or lesser extent find that Microsoft Windows is the most popular operating system chosen by their users.</div>
<div class="paddedcontent">Some of the operating systems have been grouped.  To see itemised figures for individual versions of each operating system, click the plus sign or the name of the entry.</div>